<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国 - 南华早报</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/rss/4/feed</link><description>来自中国的最新突发新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 14:21:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国国家主席习近平与俄罗斯总统普京在农历新年前通电话誓言深化两国关系</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3251447/chinese-president-xi-jinping-russias-vladimir-putin-vow-deeper-ties-phone-call-ahead-lunar-new-year?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>据央视报道，中国国家主席习近平向俄罗斯总统普京表示，两国必须“坚决反对”外部干涉，坚称需要捍卫主权、安全和发展利益。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 14:08:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3251447/chinese-president-xi-jinping-russias-vladimir-putin-vow-deeper-ties-phone-call-ahead-lunar-new-year?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>市场呼吁：尽管面临IPO挑战和双边摩擦，中国初创企业仍渴望美国投资者</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/money-wealth/article/3251427/market-call-chinese-start-ups-still-crave-us-investors-despite-ipo-challenges-bilateral-friction?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国的首次公开募股一度获得了印钞许可，但由于财务不透明、丑闻以及滴滴出行于 2022 年在纽约证券交易所突然退市而蒙上了阴影。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 14:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/money-wealth/article/3251427/market-call-chinese-start-ups-still-crave-us-investors-despite-ipo-challenges-bilateral-friction?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国国家主席习近平在农历新年前的讲话中赞扬香港和澳门一体化取得的进展</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3251445/chinas-xi-jinping-hails-progress-integrating-hong-kong-and-macau-speech-ahead-lunar-new-year?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在庆祝农历新年的年度国家聚会上，中国领导人还赞扬北京在反对“台独”和“外国势力干涉”方面取得的成功。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 13:29:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3251445/chinas-xi-jinping-hails-progress-integrating-hong-kong-and-macau-speech-ahead-lunar-new-year?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>量子突破：中国科学家用新模拟器解决了20年的物理争论</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3251440/quantum-breakthrough-chinese-scientists-settle-20-year-physics-debate-new-simulator?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国科学技术大学的研究人员使用强大的量子模拟器，依靠高质量气体来可视化可以揭示超导体机制的现象，这是“非凡且令人兴奋”的突破。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 13:00:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3251440/quantum-breakthrough-chinese-scientists-settle-20-year-physics-debate-new-simulator?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中概股下滑、美股下滑——改革能阻止潮流吗？</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3251431/china-stocks-slide-us-stocks-glide-will-reform-work-stem-tide?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>美国和中国正走在不同的经济道路上，各自的股市就是例证。在中国试图化解危机之际，专家们主张进行广泛的改革，以解决拖累经济增长和复苏前景的根本性问题。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 12:30:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3251431/china-stocks-slide-us-stocks-glide-will-reform-work-stem-tide?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国最高立法机构将讨论军队清洗中的“任免”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3251425/chinas-top-legislative-body-discuss-appointments-and-dismissals-amid-military-purge?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在高级将领和前国防部长李尚孚被免职后，全国人民代表大会常务委员会发出了进一步改组的信号。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:03:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3251425/chinas-top-legislative-body-discuss-appointments-and-dismissals-amid-military-purge?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国科学家研制出一种基于斯特林发动机的强大微波武器，可以从移动的卡车上发射</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3251381/chinese-scientists-build-powerful-stirling-engine-based-microwave-weapon-can-fire-moving-truck?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>这种高威力武器系统可以从移动的卡车上发射，并且仅使用现有方法的五分之一的能量。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3251381/chinese-scientists-build-powerful-stirling-engine-based-microwave-weapon-can-fire-moving-truck?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国谴责福岛放射性废水泄漏背后的“混乱和无序”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3251395/china-lashes-chaos-and-disorder-behind-fukushima-radioactive-waste-water-leak?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国大使馆发言人表示，这一事件“进一步凸显”释放行动需要国际监督。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 08:00:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3251395/china-lashes-chaos-and-disorder-behind-fukushima-radioactive-waste-water-leak?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装红海危机服务于中国的主要目标：削弱美国</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/article/3251355/houthi-red-sea-crisis-serves-chinas-main-goal-undermining-us?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>对于中国来说，应对当前中东危机最简单、政治上最方便的应对措施不是加入美国，而是指责美国。北京以两国方案作为解决加沙危机先决条件的立场不太可能实现，但却达到了削弱华盛顿的目的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 06:30:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/article/3251355/houthi-red-sea-crisis-serves-chinas-main-goal-undermining-us?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国种业至少落后西方巨头一代人进入“工业4.0时代”，必须加强合作</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3251294/chinas-seed-industry-lags-behind-western-giants-enter-industry-40-era-must-increase-collaboration?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国种子协会表示，海外种子巨头正在利用大数据、人工智能和基因编辑，而中国公司则专注于分子育种。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 04:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3251294/chinas-seed-industry-lags-behind-western-giants-enter-industry-40-era-must-increase-collaboration?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国通胀：随着消费者价格遭遇2009年以来最大幅度下跌，需求主导的通货再膨胀“可能仍会持续”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3251324/china-inflation-consumer-prices-fall-fourth-straight-month-january-adding-deflation-concerns?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>1月份中国消费者价格指数（CPI）连续第四个月下降，加剧了通缩困境，而出厂价格连续第16个月下降。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 01:41:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3251324/china-inflation-consumer-prices-fall-fourth-straight-month-january-adding-deflation-concerns?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>高盛报告称，中国房地产违约不会阻止银行向现金短缺的开发商提供贷款</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/business/banking-finance/article/3251298/china-property-defaults-wont-stop-banks-lending-cash-strapped-developers-says-goldman-sachs-report?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>这家美国投资银行表示，中国的房地产低迷和最近出现的一系列违约事件不太可能让海外债权人感到不安，也不会阻止国内银行向现金短缺的开发商提供资源。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 23:30:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/business/banking-finance/article/3251298/china-property-defaults-wont-stop-banks-lending-cash-strapped-developers-says-goldman-sachs-report?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国研究员龚晨光因窃取导弹跟踪技术等商业机密而被捕</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/world/united-states-canada/article/3251321/us-researcher-chenguang-gong-arrested-stealing-trade-secrets-including-missile-tracking-tech?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>据称，龚将其工作场所的 3,600 多个文件（包括用于检测核发射的传感器的蓝图）转移到个人存储设备中。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 23:09:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/world/united-states-canada/article/3251321/us-researcher-chenguang-gong-arrested-stealing-trade-secrets-including-missile-tracking-tech?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国前国防部长魏凤和缺席农历新年祝福名单引发命运质疑</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3251308/former-chinese-defence-minister-wei-fenghes-absence-lunar-new-year-greetings-list-raises-questions?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>魏忠贤的继任者李尚福去年突然被免职，其他一些高级军事人物也被免职。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 